        "testimonial_qkdHDD": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I emailed customer service because I accidentally entered the wrong apartment number. They replied the same day and fixed it before shipping. Really appreciated how easy they made everything</p>",
            "author": "Denise",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_89rrik": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>The shipping took a couple days longer than I expected, but the quality made up for it. The blouse I ordered feels much more expensive than it was. I already bookmarked a few more items for summer.</p>",
            "author": "Sharon",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_F9JjqL": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I struggle finding clothes that feel stylish without looking too young for me. Charlotte & Grace somehow has that balance. Elegant, comfortable, and flattering without trying too hard.</p>",
            "author": "Cynthia",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_chUmtU": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>The first size I ordered didn’t fit the way I wanted, but exchanging it was surprisingly simple. Customer support answered quickly and helped me choose the correct size. The new one fits perfectly</p>",
            "author": "Rebecca",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Fwmxf8": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I wore one of their maxi dresses to my friend’s birthday dinner and got compliments all night. The fit around the waist was super flattering and the material moved beautifully when walking.</p>",
            "author": "Angela",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_PKCERp": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I wish they had even more colors available in some styles because the set I bought is incredibly comfortable. It’s one of those outfits you end up reaching for constantly</p>",
            "author": "Melissa",
            "author_info": ""
          }
        }
      },
